{"tid":907594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《毒奶十年‧擴張》 【中國奶企大舉進軍海外投資奶粉廠】","createTime":"2018-11-19T02:19:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-19T15:31:16.000Z","uid":37554,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"424d7f50a57b5c6f30481feb5fb40feb0d272a9b","tid":907594,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T02:19:23.000Z","msg":"毒奶事件後，除了中國本土乳業面臨重整，不少涉及三聚氰胺事件的奶企也大舉進軍海外，包括到乳業大國新西蘭併購奶廠和牧場，再將產品反銷中國，欲重奪被外國品牌佔據的奶粉市場。<br />\n<br />\n中國對外國奶粉的需求，也推動新西蘭的乳業急促發展。2008年後，新西蘭奶價飆升，當地的農場亦不斷擴張。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/757931034556352/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F757931034556352%2F&d=pZBVOThsalqHuy22W8pBzMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=b74bf3a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/757931034556352/</a>"},{"pid":"a5d61be1fe1db9ef8a02c43ab6683f4ffa1bd2f4","tid":907594,"uid":35814,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T02:30:38.000Z","msg":"將三聚氰胺嘅好處帶到世界各地<br />\n全球人口控制計劃<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddbc7b9912ebced4f1d4974328d81ca6fb02f327","tid":907594,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5d61be1fe1db9ef8a02c43ab6683f4ffa1bd2f4","tid":907594,"uid":35814,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T02:30:38.000Z","msg":"將三聚氰胺嘅好處帶到世界各地<br />\n全球人口控制計劃<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T02:43:25.000Z","msg":"人地資訊咁透明呃唔到人啦，賣返去中國就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0abc380b13165de0949aba9b7d6cd7248c600ff","tid":907594,"uid":14083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T02:54:48.000Z","msg":"而加大陸公司好興係外國manufacture， 之後扮外國brand 再加啲marketing 有幾勁有幾多年歷史，有幾多科學根據呀當然全部係吹啦，再ship返大陸賣，而啲貨正係大陸先買到大家放心"},{"pid":"597dd0dc3815b8d9bbb7aaa8c697449add29b671","tid"